title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Every minute was more exciting than the next. [From an on-camera interview with Linda Evans, commenting on “Night of 100 Stars” partly in New York to promote “Lifestyles of the Rich & Famous.”]
